OL,3,CDesperate retirees left without
OL,4,Cpension payments due to new IT system
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FPensioners across the West Midlands
OL,8,Fwho have waited for months on end for
OL,9,Ftheir payments have told they are
OL,10,Fstruggling with their mental health as
OL,11,Fthey are forced to borrow money and
OL,12,Flive off savings.
OL,14,FThis desperate fate is thought to be
OL,15,Faffecting around 2,000 people, who
OL,16,Fworked in the - as a result of payout
OL,17,Fdelays caused by a new IT system at
OL,18,Fthe Pension Fund.
