OL,7,FWest Midlands Pension Fund said the
OL,8,Fdelays were due to an computer system
OL,9,Fupgrade that took place last July.
OL,11,FBut months on and the issue is still
OL,12,Faffecting thousands of people.
OL,14,FRetirees have reached out to ITV
OL,15,FCentral to share their devastation at
OL,16,Fbeing left without the money they
OL,17,Fsaved throughout their lives.
OL,19,FAmanda Clayton, from Quarry Bank,
OL,20,Fretired last August from her job as a
OL,21,Fhigher level teaching assistant.
