OL,7,FShe has yet to see a penny from the
OL,8,Fpension fund she paid into for more
OL,9,Fthan 20 years.
OL,11,FAmanda is one of many impacted by the
OL,12,Fdelays - as a result of issues from
OL,13,Fthe organisation that manages the
OL,14,Fpensions of 350,000 people in the West
OL,15,FMidlands - from 800 public sector
OL,16,Forganisations.
