OL,7,FShe said she has called the Fund's
OL,8,Fhelpline, which is open for just five
OL,9,Fhours a day, with a average call
OL,10,Fwaiting time of 45 minutes, but she is
OL,11,Funable to access the information she
OL,12,Fneeds.
OL,14,FShe said: "They are not talking to
OL,15,Fpeople, they don't come back to you.
OL,17,F"It has been so stressful it is to
OL,18,Faccess something that is rightfully
OL,19,Fyours. There have been times that I've
OL,20,Fcome off the phone and I have been in
OL,21,Ftears."
