OL,7,FDebbie Mitchell, a former council
OL,8,Fworker from Cosford, decided to cash
OL,9,Fin her pension last year after
OL,10,Fexperiencing health concerns.
OL,12,FShe said before the IT system was
OL,13,Fchanged, she was told it would take
OL,14,Faround six weeks to get her pension
OL,15,Fcashed in.
OL,17,FHowever, she submitted her application
OL,18,Fafter the IT system was changed and
OL,19,Fhas now been forced to use her savings
OL,20,Fwhile she waits for her money.
