OL,7,FShe said: "I've always been quite
OL,8,Findependent, so not having my own
OL,9,Fmoney has been quite difficult
OL,10,Factually. I don't like having to
OL,11,Fborrow off my husband or use credit
OL,12,Fcards.
OL,14,F"For 31 years I've paid into the Fund,
OL,15,FI've always been quite self-
OL,16,Fsufficient. I'm now living on no money
OL,17,Fof my own."
OL,19,FITV Central has heard the
OL,20,Fheartbreaking stories from several of
OL,21,Fthose affected.
