OL,7,FIn December 2023, a pensioner told of
OL,8,Fhis wait for money from the Fund that
OL,9,Fhe had paid into during his employment.
OL,11,FSince then, many more have contacted
OL,12,Fto share their experiences about the
OL,13,Fnightmare they have faced.
OL,15,FOne person said: "Once retired I will
OL,16,Fhave no other form of income and this
OL,17,Fis resulting in an immense amount of
OL,18,Fpersonal stress."
