OL,7,FAnother added: "I am upset as the
OL,8,Fwhole idea of me taking my pension
OL,9,Fearly was so that it supplemented my
OL,10,Fincome as I have had to work part time
OL,11,Fdue to ill health."
OL,13,FSomeone else said: "I have been trying
OL,14,Fsince September to access my pension.
OL,15,FI decided to borrow #3000 pounds from
OL,16,Fmy bank to tide me over.
OL,18,F"I know there are some much worse off
OL,19,Fthan me but it's my money. How long
OL,20,Fwill I have to wait?"
