OL,7,FWest Midlands Pension Fund has
OL,8,Facknowledged what it calls a "drop in
OL,9,Fservice delivery performance"
OL,11,FIn a statement it said: "We would like
OL,12,Fto reassure our members and employers,
OL,13,Fthat we are making progress in
OL,14,Frecovering our service standards.
OL,16,F"We remain focussed on servicing those
OL,17,Fmembers who are seeking and waiting
OL,18,Ffor retirement benefit quotations,
OL,19,Fpayments and beneficiary benefits,
OL,20,Fprioritising those most in need and
OL,21,Freducing aged casework.
