OL,7,F"We would like to thank our members
OL,8,Fand employers for their ongoing
OL,9,Fpatience, support and understanding at
OL,10,Fthis time."
OL,12,FThe West Midlands Mayor Andy Street
OL,13,Ftold ITV Central he has been assured
OL,14,Fby the WMPF the system is improving.
OL,16,FHe said: "I have been pressing them to
OL,17,Fget it solved as quickly as possible
OL,18,Fand really clearly getting an answer
OL,19,Fto those people who are waiting for
OL,20,Ftheir estimates, thinking about where
OL,21,Fthey take.
